  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">We’re introducing an exciting commission discount to help you sell more and earn more across France, Spain and the UK!</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Promo Dates</strong></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">France &amp; Spain: 15 March 2026, 00:00 CET - 31 March 2026, 23:59 CET</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">UK: Starting 1 April</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">, 11:59 PM CET</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">How it works</span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">France (backmarket.fr) &amp; Spain (backmarket.es)</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Eligible models</strong>: This campaign is focused on a mix of iPhone and Samsung Galaxy models.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To qualify for the commission discount, you need to meet the following criteria:</span></p>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Base commission discount</strong>: Earn a 3% commission discount on eligible models sold below the recommended maximum prices in either France or Spain.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Volume incentives (calculated across the total promotion period):</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong></strong></span></li></ol>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </p>\n<table style=\"width: 601.991px;height: 169.681px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 142px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 251px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 209px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 34.5694px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #111418;\">iPhone</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #111418;\">Samsung Galaxy<br></span></strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7778px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">3% discount</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">Matching the recommended price</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\"></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7778px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">-1% extra</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">100 units</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">100 units<br></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7778px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">-1% extra</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">400 units</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">250 units<br></span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Only units sold on eligible models during the campaign period count towards the volume incentive.</p>\n<ol start=\"3\"><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Maximum discount</strong>: The highest possible commission discount is 5%.</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></li></ol>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#128204; </span></span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aTC-tdiYCUxQy2qJyqZNfdwhFf7tEna4pl-yFAx-gY4/edit?gid=784169896#gid=784169896\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: #2980b9;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Find the list of eligible models and their recommended maximum prices here</span></span></strong></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">UK (backmarket.co.uk)</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Eligible models</strong>: A selection of Smartphones, iPads and Macbooks (see link for full list and recommended maximum prices)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To qualify for the commission discount, you need to meet the following criteria:</span></p>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Base commission discount</strong>: Earn a 3% commission discount on eligible models sold below the recommended maximum prices in the UK.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Volume-based extra discount</strong>:</span>\n<table style=\"width: 602px;height: 169.703px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 167px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 191px;\"></col><col style=\"width: 243px;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 34.5781px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\"></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #111418;\">Smartphones</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #111418;\">MacBooks/iPads/Consoles </span></strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7812px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">3% discount</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">Matching the recommended price</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7812px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">-1% extra</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">60 units</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">40 units</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7812px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">-1% extra</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">280 units</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">160 units</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.7812px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">-1% extra</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">650 units</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #111418;\">400 units</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\nOnly orders shipped of eligible models during the campaign period count towards the volume incentive.</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Maximum discount</strong>: The highest possible commission discount is 6%.</span></li></ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #2980b9;\">&#128204; <strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1lwsh8m1pghz01sGxNfsf3QkKS