ca, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Total commission discount on eligible models</span></strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37.3333px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Seller A</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">0-59</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">-3%</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37.3333px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Seller B</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">60-279</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">-4%</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37.3333px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Seller C</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">280-649</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">-5%</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Seller C</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">&gt;650</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">-6%</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 37.3333px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Seller D</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">❌</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">500</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">0%</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you sell 800 units of iPhone 13, with 200 sold at or below the recommended target price and 1800 units sold above the target price, you will qualify for the maximum 6% commission discount. However, the 6% discount applies only to the 200 units sold at or below the target price. The 1800 units sold above the target price will not qualify for any discount.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Weekly target price updates</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">During the extension period, target prices will be updated weekly on your Back-office to reflect market conditions.</span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Updated every Wednesday for France &amp; Spain</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Updated every 2 weeks on Tuesday for UK</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">New prices take effect on Thursdays at 00:00 CET</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Please ensure your prices remain below the current target prices to qualify for discounts.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Commission refund process</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Your regular commission will be invoiced weekly as usual.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">After the promotion ends, the total commission discount earned will be refunded to you on:</span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">8 April 2026 for France &amp; Spain</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">UK: </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">14 January 2026</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In case of recommended maximum prices adjustment during the period, the units you have sold at or below the previous maximum recommended prices since the campaign began will still count toward unlocking extra commission discounts based on volume.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Why participate?</span></h2>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Increase your margins</strong>: Reduce your commission costs and keep more of your revenue.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Stay competitive</strong>: Benefit from greater visibility and a stronger position on Back Market.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Drive higher sales</strong>: More attractive pricing leads to increased customer demand and higher sales volume.</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Next steps</span></h2>\n<ol><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Source the eligible models if you don’t have them already and list them on our platform.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ensure your selling prices remain below the recommended maximum prices.</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Track your sales volume to see if you qualify for the extra commission discounts.</span></li></ol>"
}